{
  "stem": "5470.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hohal, ?] and from there to [INAUDIBLE], over to [INAUDIBLE] rest of them [INAUDIBLE] in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he went straight away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After he saw them leaving, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Slazinger ?] watched them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as soon as they were out of sight, he moved over to my office and handed me over what he had gotten by Gemmecker to him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was a pistol-- just a tiny pistol.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Just the size of your hand, pocket one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "About 4.3 millimeter, something like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A tiny one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And in that fact, he actually handed over the command to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And from there on, the Germans, as soon as the, uh-- the staff moved out, the watch people-- the [GERMAN] Polizei opened the gate and went to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, um, that's where I took over and put my men, the Jewish people, and closed the gate again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I went straightaway into conference with, uh-- I said I will do it, to take over the command.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I'm still young, and I don't want to do it on my own.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I appointed straightaway six elderly people as my advisors around me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And with those people, I went into a-- a meeting, and that took the whole night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And well, my wife was still on the outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I brought her in, because we had quite a lot to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These German people were-- which were in the inside of the camp still-- those [GERMAN] Polizei-- what was I going to do with those people?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had the commander there, and we had further discussions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as they said in that period of time, we had 120 non-Jewish people in the camp also.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
